[SN]TITLE[SN]
Pro12: Treviso 27-11 Newport Gwent Dragons

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Treviso scored three tries to earn their first win of the season and condemn Newport Gwent Dragons to a third defeat from four Pro12 games.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
